<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作品打分</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b75b8221cd844b86941a89ade61806f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>问题分析与讲解</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a39f09488dc8475b935b396721e420e3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>考核作品展示</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/447ecd4036b44b66a8fb10d7de4c87b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/eb2373c04d8a4c65abad43d3d6f9b017.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7bd8ba61798d4da889d690d0e5cedd25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5ccb416f4e454d2696bf6fd3d8f0f666.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
